dct_description_sm: New Jersey Deparment of Conservation and Economic Development. Division of Planning and Development. Atlas Sheet 29 (1950) New Jersey Geological Survey. Alternate title: [New Jersey.] Atlas sheet no. 29. Relief shown by 10 ft. contour interval and spot heights. Depth of water shown by fathom in feet at low tide. Title is not given. Region covered: Monmouth Shore. Original survey made under the direction of C. C. Vermeule, Topographer in 1880-3,. 1950 revision by R. G. Blanchard, Topographic Engineer.
dct_publisher_sm: Trenton, N.J. : New Jersey Geological Survey, 1950.
